---
import BaseLayout from '../../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout
  title="About & Contact — Rabbit Logs"
  description="Not a coder — the view of someone who runs the system. Field notes on SAP from a practitioner's eyes."
  lang="en"
>
  <article class="prose page about">
    <div class="about-hero">
      <img src="/about-logo.png" alt="Rabbit Logs mascot" class="about-logo" />
      <h1>Welcome to Rabbit Logs</h1>
      <p class="tagline">Not a coder — the view of someone who runs the system.</p>
    </div>

    <p class="lead">As a production-management practitioner,<br />I worked on a production PI project and an SAP PP build,<br />carried it through stabilization and enhancement projects,<br />and today I bring that experience into day-to-day operations.</p>

    <p class="lead">This is a space where SAP is recorded and organized<br />through <strong>a practitioner's eyes</strong>, not a developer's language.</p>

    <div class="motto">
      <p class="motto-main">Process over features, people over screens.</p>
      <p class="motto-sub">Sharing what actually helps in real work.</p>
    </div>

    <h2>📬 Contact</h2>

    <p>Have a question or something to share? Feel free to email me — I usually reply within a few days.</p>

    <p class="contact-box">
      <span class="contact-label">E-mail</span>
      <a href="mailto:contact@rabbitlogs.com" class="contact-mail">contact@rabbitlogs.com</a>
    </p>
  </article>

  <style>
    .about { max-width: 640px; }
    .about-hero { text-align: center; margin: 0.5rem 0 1.8rem; }
    .about-logo { width: 110px; height: auto; margin: 0 auto 0.8rem; display: block; }
    .about-hero h1 { font-weight: 800; font-size: 1.6rem; letter-spacing: -0.02em; margin: 0 0 0.5rem; }
    .tagline { color: var(--muted); font-size: 1rem; margin: 0; }

    .about .lead { font-size: 1.02rem; line-height: 1.8; color: var(--ink); margin: 1.2rem 0; text-align: center; }
    .about .lead strong { color: var(--primary); font-weight: 700; }

    .motto { text-align: center; margin: 1.8rem 0; padding: 1.3rem 0; border-top: 1px solid var(--line); border-bottom: 1px solid var(--line); }
    .motto-main { font-size: 1.2rem; font-weight: 700; color: var(--primary); line-height: 1.6; margin: 0; letter-spacing: -0.01em; }
    .motto-sub { font-size: 0.96rem; color: var(--muted); margin: 0.6rem 0 0; }

    .about h2 { font-size: 1.2rem; margin-top: 1.8rem; margin-bottom: 0.6rem; text-align: center; }
    .about > p:not([class]) { text-align: center; margin: 0.8rem 0; }
    .contact-box {
      display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center; gap: 0.9rem;
      background: var(--color-bg-soft); border: 1px solid var(--line);
      border-radius: 10px; padding: 0.9rem 1.25rem; margin: 1rem 0;
    }
    .contact-label {
      font-size: 0.78rem; font-weight: 700; color: #fff; background: var(--primary);
      padding: 0.22rem 0.6rem; border-radius: 6px; letter-spacing: 0.03em; white-space: nowrap;
    }
    .contact-mail { font-weight: 600; font-size: 1.05rem; }
  </style>
</BaseLayout>
